{"tid":1696040,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"為何沒有破窗效應","createTime":"2019-11-06T03:03:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-06T04:32:13.000Z","uid":39683,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9c49c5b3ecee50f68d38b8183306dd70ce01f7","tid":1696040,"uid":39683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:03:44.000Z","msg":"破窗效應（英語：Broken windows theory）是心理學理論，由詹姆士&middot;威爾遜及喬治&middot;凱林（George L. Kelling）提出，刊載於《The Atlantic Monthly》1982年3月版的一篇題為《Broken Windows》的文章上[1]，論及環境中的不良現象如果被放任存在，就會誘使人們仿效，甚至變本加厲。<br />\n<br />\n斬警又話假，斬何妖又話假，自己封咗個窗先，咁仲邊有人想做<br />\n<br />\n斬對家嘅不論真假應全力鼓勵，以英雄相稱<br />\n<br />\n義士鼓起勇氣做你地唔敢做嘅野仲要比你地話假，呢啲無名英雄聽審嘅人都未必有，仲一定坐好耐，點解要極速割<br />\n<br />\n泛民，民陣比人打，啲濕尻藍絲都係話佢地自編自導咋，你地同濕尻藍絲有乜分別<br />\n<br />\n仲要冷處理義士？話佢廢？在座各位見到何妖連打佢都唔敢啦，有乜資格割<br />\n只敢喺連登打字話好嬲，見到警察調頭走嘅人有乜資格話做實事嘅人假"},{"pid":"c89b92695c695f1869f5a8bdbe8408e48bd8672c","tid":1696040,"uid":29080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:15:28.000Z","msg":"口說不割<br />\n實際就一聽到已經彈九丈遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9127464480aed95fa8ec2faba83c6c5e2479e665","tid":1696040,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:18:05.000Z","msg":"鄭立又黎教連登仔女做人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1696044\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1696044</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa62abe86ab7e21b71196ea825c447904df606ca","tid":1696040,"uid":63543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"斬死左就唔會當假<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"809e4f25be8c6e8785c090f8e1c8ba3f72c3a8a5","tid":1696040,"uid":39683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"aa62abe86ab7e21b71196ea825c447904df606ca","tid":1696040,"uid":63543,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"斬死左就唔會當假<img src=\"/assets/fac